<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="JavaScript- Counter">
    <title>Countdown</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/img/favicon.png">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&family=Open+Sans:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/main.css">
</head>

<body>
    <main class="hero">
        <figure class="hero__image">
            <img src="img/hero.jpeg" alt="Hero image">
        </figure>
        <div class="hero__content">
            <div class="hero__content__title">Old Iphone Giveaway</div>
            <div class="hero__content__subtitle js-giveaway">
                Giveaway Ends On <time>Sunday, 13 June 2021 11:30 am</time>
            </div>
            <p class="hero__content__desc">
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Expedita nulla hic doloremque assumenda, voluptatum quasi ipsam molestiae a. Nobis, natus? Inventore veniam non consectetur perspiciatis earum alias voluptas distinctio rerum!
            </p>
            <div class="timer js-timer">
                <div class="timer__item">
                    <span class="timer__item__value js-timerValue">14</span>
                    <span class="timer__item__title">days</span>
                </div>
                <div class="timer__item">
                    <span class="timer__item__value js-timerValue">17</span>
                    <span class="timer__item__title">hours</span>
                </div>
                <div class="timer__item">
                    <span class="timer__item__value js-timerValue">45</span>
                    <span class="timer__item__title">mins</span>
                </div>
                <div class="timer__item">
                    <span class="timer__item__value js-timerValue">24</span>
                    <span class="timer__item__title">secs</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <script src="js/main.js"></script>
</body>

</html>